                "name": "Treat Disease",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "text": "You spend at least 8 hours caring for a diseased creature. Attempt a Medicine check against the disease's DC. After you attempt to Treat a Disease for a creature, you can't try again until after that creature's next save against the disease.",
